Cell["\<\
This graph is interesting. Mainly because the \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]wave\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] behavior that we\[CloseCurlyQuote]ve been seeing in \
previous problems isn\[CloseCurlyQuote]t too prominent, and because the \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]pillar\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] behavior we\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]ve seen in the heat equation is the more dominant feature. \
\
\>", "Text",
