  FormatType->"TraditionalForm",ExpressionUUID->
  "5b75240c-b82b-4225-ac9f-e887bb9dcb2a"],
 " on [-1,1] with the weight function w(x)=1. Are these polynomials simply \
orthogonal or are they orthonormal? Explain why. "
}], "Section",
